### Monitoring API Testbestand
# Dit bestand werkt direct in VS Code (met de "REST Client" extensie) of JetBrains IDEs.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Test V1 Status Endpoint
GET {{host}}/api/v1/status
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Test V2 Status Endpoint
GET {{host}}/api/v2/status
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. List kunstwerken (lookup)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/kunstwerken
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get sensoren for a kunstwerk (lookup)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/kunstwerken/1/sensoren
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get all metingen for a kunstwerk
GET {{host}}/api/v1/metingen/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get most recent meting per sensor for a kunstwerk
GET {{host}}/api/v1/metingen/1/recent
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Get all afwijkingen for a kunstwerk
GET {{host}}/api/v1/afwijkingen/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Create a manual meting (inspecteur)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/meting
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "sensorId": 1,
  "kunstwerkId": 1,
  "waarde": 12.34
}

###

### Notes
# - Pas `sensorId` en `kunstwerkId` aan naar bestaande testwaarden in je DB.
# - Gebruik de VS Code REST Client of `curl` om de requests te verzenden.